task.summary: 2.2.43 : Websocket: added replaceOnDuplicate. Cache: renamed exists for contains.
2.2.44 : Fixed TCP commands queue (in some cases it was looping)
2.2.45 : Smtp settings override improved. Query code cleaned
2.2.50 : Config.getDbl added, Log rotate added. Fixed SysService argument management. Added HMCA in crypt
2.2.53 : Fixed SQLite and Log/Config initialization errors
2.3.4 : Added DateTime to get() and where()
2.3.7 : log.level in Config was not properly loaded
2.4.0 Changed addAutoComplete for updateAutoComplete in Console
2.4.4 Changed the way onInit works in Consoles
2.4.5 Bug Fix: Logs being printed on screen even when log.file is set.
2.4.5 Console: after password prompt, clear buffer and call garbage collection
2.4.6 Crypt stable. Added System.console when no mask is specified in Console
2.4.6 : Zip log files if class is present
2.4.6 : Added tests for Zip logs. Some code was further split inside Log. Added Log.enable
2.4.7 : Moved SysMain and SysService to core
2.4.9 : Added JarResource and logs should be printed when SNAPSHOT is used.
2.4.10 : Do not log stderr by default. Allow unlimited wait time in commands.
2.4.11 : WebService runs in foreground as default. Automatically detects absolute paths. Correct services path if required.
